
They hadn't seen what had happened to Kali when she returned, only the aftermath. But there had been a faint, lingering scent of someone else. Another demon.
What had dads told Kali last night?
Lio lifted an index finger. "You two continue to argue as you were. Carmi, continue berating him. I'm going to ring up a gentleman."



